, detailed audit logging"}],["$","p","293",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["<pre class=\"code-block\"><code>"]}],["$","p","294",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["tier: T2"]}],["$","p","295",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["warrant_validity: \"15min\""]}],["$","p","296",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["approval_required: \"conditional\" # Based on policy"]}],["$","p","297",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["constraints: [\"mfa_required\", \"detailed_audit\", \"rollback_plan\"]"]}],["$","p","298",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["</code></pre>"]}],["$","br","299",{}],["$","p","300",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["#### ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"T3 - High-Risk Operations"}],""]}],["$","li","301",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Examples**: System administration, bulk operations, irreversible actions"}],["$","li","302",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Governance**: Ultra-strict warrant, 5min validity, always requires human approval"}],["$","li","303",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Constraints**: Multi-person approval, complete audit trail, mandatory rollback plan"}],["$","p","304",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["<pre class=\"code-block\"><code>"]}],["$","p","305",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["tier: T3"]}],["$","p","306",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["warrant_validity: \"5min\""]}],["$","p","307",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["approval_required: \"always\""]}],["$","p","308",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed m