me":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["// Zero-trust approach:"]}],["$","p","329",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["const intent = await vienna.submitIntent({"]}],["$","p","330",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["action: \"stripe.refund.create\","]}],["$","p","331",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["target: orderId,"]}],["$","p","332",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["parameters: { amount, reason },"]}],["$","p","333",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["agent_id: process.env.AGENT_ID,"]}],["$","p","334",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["justification: `Customer refund: ${reason}`"]}],["$","p","335",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["});"]}],["$","br","336",{}],["$","p","337",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["if (intent.status === 'approved') {"]}],["$","p","338",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["return await vienna.execute(intent.warrant_id);"]}],["$","p","339",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["} else if (intent.status === 'requires_approval') {"]}],["$","p","340",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["return { status: 'pending', approval_url: intent.approval_url };"]}],["$","p","341",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["} else {"]}],["$","p","342",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["throw new Error(`Intent denied: ${intent.denial_reason}`);"]}],["$","p","343",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["}"]}],["$","p","344",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["}"]}],["$","p","345",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["</code></pre>"]}],["$","br","346",{}],["$","h2","347",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Implementation Checklist"}],["$","br","348",{}],["$","h3","349",{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"Phase 1: Assessment and Planning (Week 1)"}],["$","li","350",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Inventory existing agent permissions** - What APIs do your agents access?"}],["$","li","351",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Map business rules to policies** - What constraints should apply?"}],["$","li","352",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Identify high-risk operations** - What needs human approval?"}],["$","li","353",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Set up Vienna OS environment** - Deploy governance infrastructure"}],["$","br","354",{}],["$","h3","355",{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"Phase 2: Policy Development (Week 2)"}],["$","li","356",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Write intent schemas** - Define allowed actions and parameters"}],["$","li","357",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Create policy framework** - Implement business rules as code"}],["$","li","358",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Configure risk tiers** - Classify operations by impact (T0-T3)"}],["$","li","359",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Set up approval workflows** - Define who approves what"}],["$","br","360",{}],["$","h3","361",{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"Phase 3: Agent Integration (Week 3-4)"}],["$","li","362",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Install Vienna OS SDK** - Integrate with existing agent code"}],["$","li","363",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Replace direct API calls** - Convert to intent-based pattern"}],["$","li","364",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Add warrant verification** - Protect your services"}],["$","li","365",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Implement attestation logging** - Track all governed actions"}],["$","br","366",{}],["$","h3","367",{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"Phase 4: Testing and Rollout (Week 5-6)"}],["$","li","368",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Test policy edge cases** - What happens when things go wrong?"}],["$","li","369",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Load test warrant validation** - Ensure performance under load"}],["$","li","370",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Train operations team** - Who monitors and responds to alerts?"}],["$","li","371",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Gradual rollout** - Start with low-risk operations"}],["$","br","372",{}],["$","h3","373",{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"Phase 5: Monitoring and Optimization (Ongoing)"}],["$","li","374",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Monitor policy effectiveness** - Are rules catching problems?"}],["$","li","375",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Tune performance** - Optimize warrant validation times"}],["$","li","376",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Refine risk tiers** - Adjust T0-T3 classifications based on experience"}],["$","li","377",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"[ ] **Regular policy review** - Keep rules current with business needs"}],["$","br","378",{}],["$","h2","379",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Conclusion"}],["$","br","380",{}],["$","p","381",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Zero-trust architecture isn't just a security buzzword—it's the only viable approach for governing AI agents at scale. When your agents have the power to affect real business outcomes, \"trust but verify\" becomes \"trust and pray.\" Vienna OS provides the governance infrastructure to never trust, always verify, every action, every time."]}],["$","br","382",{}],["$","p","383",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"*The zero trust ai approach delivers:*"}],["$","li","384",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Reduced risk**: Time-bound warrants limit blast radius"}],["$","li","385",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Better compliance**: Cryptographic audit trails satisfy regulators"}],["$","li","386",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Operational visibility**: See everything your agents do in real-time"}],["$","li","387",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Business rule enforcement**: Policies are code, not hope"}],["$","li","388",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"**Incident response**: Surgical response instead of nuclear shutdown"}],["$","br","389",{}],["$","p","390",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Traditional security assumed humans were making decisions. Zero-trust for AI assumes agents are making decisions—and puts the right guardrails in place."]}],["$","br","391",{}],["$","hr","392",{"className":"border-navy-700 my-8"}],["$","br","393",{}],["$","p","394",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"*Ready to implement zero-trust for your AI agents?*"}],["$","br","395",{}],["$","p","396",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Start with a [free Vienna OS trial](https://console.regulator.ai) or explore our [documentation](/docs) to see how intent-based governance works. For technical discussions, join our community on [GitHub](https://github.com/vienna-os/vienna-os) or book a [demo call](/try)."]}],["$","br","397",{}],["$","p","398",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Your agents are already making decisions. Make sure they're making the right ones."]}]]}],["$","$Lf",null,{"slug":"zero-trust-ai-agent-pipeline"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12","children":["$","$L10",null,{"variant":"compact","showSocialProof":true,"className":"max-w-lg mx-auto"}]}]]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"border-t border-navy-700 py-8 mt-12","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"/blog","className":"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition mb-4","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4","children":[["$","path","1l729n",{"d":"m12 19-7-7 7-7"}],["$","path","x3x0zl",{"d":"M19 12H5"}],"$undefined"]}],"Back to Blog"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs text-slate-600","children":"© 2026 Technetwork 2 LLC dba ai.ventures. All rights reserved."}]]}]}]]}]
